<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: broken ceramics -->
  <DMS_BrokenCeramics.label>破碎陶瓷</DMS_BrokenCeramics.label>
  
  <!-- EN: ceramic plates -->
  <DMS_CeramicsPlating.label>拋棄式陶瓷裝甲</DMS_CeramicsPlating.label>
  <!-- EN: A set of ceramic plates can be mounted on the mech's external shell to provide additional protection, but once damaged it can only be replaced with a new one. \n\nThe maximum amount of the plating on mech can apply depends on its body size. -->
  <DMS_CeramicsPlating.description>一組拋棄式陶瓷裝甲板與安裝用的支架和工具組等，陶瓷裝甲板可以安裝在機兵的機體上以提供額外的防護，但一經損壞就只能更換新的。 \n\n最大可安裝數量取決於安裝機體的體型。</DMS_CeramicsPlating.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <DMS_CeramicsPlating.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>安裝{0}</DMS_CeramicsPlating.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: nuclear battery -->
  <DMS_NuclearBattery.label>裂變電池</DMS_NuclearBattery.label>
  <!-- EN: A nuclear fission battery with a simple structure, commonly found in many unmanned signal stations and defense robots, consists of six high-density uranium-235 columns near critical mass and thermocouples integrated and wrapped in a high-strength shell. Its energy is enough to make most models of automatroid operate for decades. -->
  <DMS_NuclearBattery.description>一種結構簡單的核裂變電池，常見於許多無人職守的訊號站與駐防用的機兵上，由六根接近臨界質量的柱狀高密度鈾235與熱電偶集成並包裹在一個高強度殼體中。其輸出的能量足夠讓絕大部分型號的機兵運轉長達數百年，並且在緊急情況下也可以變為一次性核彈使用。</DMS_NuclearBattery.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <DMS_NuclearBattery.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>安裝{0}</DMS_NuclearBattery.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: reinforced frame -->
  <DMS_ReinforcedFrame.label>強化骨架</DMS_ReinforcedFrame.label>
  <!-- EN: A set of tungsteel frame to replace parts that are prone to wear can effectively improve the durability during high-intensity combat and reduce the time spent on maintenance. But in exchange it will significantly increase the weight of the mech and affect its speed -->
  <DMS_ReinforcedFrame.description>使用鎢鋼合金來替換機兵骨架中較易磨損的部位，這可以有效提高在高強度戰鬥時的耐用性並且能在火力壓制下也不受干擾的行動。但作為代價會顯著提高機兵的重量並影響速度。</DMS_ReinforcedFrame.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <DMS_ReinforcedFrame.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>安裝{0}</DMS_ReinforcedFrame.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  
</LanguageData>